Naomi Jacobson bụ onye na-akpụ ihe

A mụrụ ya na Windhoek na South West Africa n'ubochí izizi n'ọnwa Juun n'afọ 1925. Nna ya bụ Israel Goldblatt, onye ọka iwu na onye na-akwado nnwere onwe Namibia. Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum nke Cape Town ebe ọ zutere ma lụọ di ya Larry

Ha kwagara Johannesburg n'afọ 1973. N'oge ọrụ ya, o mere ihe oyiyi nke ndị mmadụ gụnyere Lord Baden-Powell, Nelson Mandela, Oliver Tambo, ndị eze Zulu Shaka na Cetshwayo, Steve Biko, na Sir Seretse Khama. Ọ nwụrụ n'afọ 2016.
